ARTEFACT_ID: {{ARTEFACT_ID}}
  generated:       {{GENERATED_AT}} UTC
  method:          SHA-256 of (source_type + date + artefact content), first 8 hex chars
  zotero_item_type: {{ZOTERO_ITEM_TYPE}}
  type_tag:        {{TYPE_TAG}}
  schema_version:  1.0
  prompt_version:  1.0

The model must use ARTEFACT_ID verbatim as source_id and TYPE_TAG verbatim
in the Zotero tag list. Do not generate, modify, or interpret these values.

